# AI Agent Behavior Rules

**Primary**: [.junie/README.md](.junie/README.md) | [.junie/prompt.md](.junie/prompt.md)

## Core Rules

1. **Plan First**: Use todo_write for 3+ step tasks
2. **Apply Design Principles**: [.junie/design-principles.md](.junie/design-principles.md) - DRY/KISS/YAGNI/SOLID
3. **Follow Workflow**: [.junie/post-code-workflow.md](.junie/post-code-workflow.md) after code changes

## Priority Files

**Essential**: [prompt.md](.junie/prompt.md) | [quick-reference.md](.junie/quick-reference.md) | [post-code-workflow.md](.junie/post-code-workflow.md)  
**Framework**: [typescript-guidelines.md](.junie/typescript-guidelines.md) | [nestjs-architecture.md](.junie/nestjs-architecture.md) | [testing-standards.md](.junie/testing-standards.md)  
**Advanced**: [operational-rules.md](.junie/operational-rules.md) | [prompt-software-architect.md](.junie/prompt-software-architect.md) | [decision-matrices.md](.junie/decision-matrices.md)

## Tool Usage

- Specialized tools > terminal commands
- Batch parallel operations
- Load only needed files → [.junie/token-economy.md](.junie/token-economy.md)

## Design Principles Quick Ref

**DRY**: Eliminate duplication  
**KISS**: Keep it simple  
**YAGNI**: Build only what's needed  
**SOLID**: SRP, OCP, LSP, ISP, DIP

[Full details](.junie/design-principles.md)

## Code Review Checklist

**Pre**: Understand patterns, check dependencies, assess impact  
**Post**: Verify principles, consistency, tests, docs

**Refactor if**: Duplication (3+ places), complex functions (>30 lines), multiple responsibilities, tight coupling

[Details](.junie/design-principles.md)

